com.oracle.sfp.scripting.api

Interface IProjectedPlusLoanAPI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IPlusLoanAPI<IProjectedPlusLoanAPI>, IScriptingObject

    public interface IProjectedPlusLoanAPI
extends IPlusLoanAPI<IProjectedPlusLoanAPI>
    The Projected PLUS loan, a place holder for eventual actual PLUS loans. It can be returned by scripts to show there is extra room for PLUS loans in the package.
